node.text: Unbox the Pink Box is back to celebrate breakfast week at Crumbl! Join Crumbl HQ's Brelynn and Gabe as they share the cookies' backstories on each flavor and rank their favorites!

Welcome to our Crumbl summer fair week! Join Brelynn and Gabe from Crumbl HQ unbox this week's pink box, sharing their favorites, and kicking off this week's Crumbl Fair Game. 🎡💕
 
In addition to bringing fair flavored cookies, we will be hosting our own Crumbl Fair Game! Listen closely in this episode for your FIRST hint in our fair game, then stay tuned as we share a new hint each day on one of our social media platforms! 

The platform will switch daily so make sure you are paying close attention, to gather all the clues. Keep an eye out on Friday for where you should submit your final answer! The first FIVE people to put together the clues win a swag bag! Who's ready to CRUMBL?! 😉🍪

COOKIES FOR BREAKFAST? I think yes! 😍

September 6 - 11: (OPEN ON LABOR DAY)

🧇 WAFFLE
A thick waffle cookie drizzled with rich maple syrup and topped with a dollop of sweet buttercream frosting. 

🍩 OLD FASHIONED DOUGHNUT (NEW)
A warm cake cookie with flavors of vanilla, butter and spice and topped with a creamy glaze.

🍌 BANANA BREAD
A warm banana cookie with hints of vanilla, topped with a cream cheese glaze and a generous sprinkle of brown sugar crumbs.

🥛 CEREAL MILK SANDWICH FT. PEBBLES® CEREAL (NEW)
Two chilled sugar cookies rolled in Fruity PEBBLES®, sandwiching a Fruity PEBBLES cereal milk mousse.

🍭 CLASSIC SUGAR
Our classic sugar cookie base topped with a perfect pink swirl of almond-flavored frosting.  🍪 MILK CHOCOLATE
An award-winning warm cookie with milk chocolate chips.

🚨 GIVEAWAY CLOSED🚨
Like & tag three friends on this post 👇 for a chance to win a FREE party box! We will announce the winner tomorrow on our story.

#TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies #PinkBox

📲 www.crumbl.com/app
